message.text:
Stage of endless possibilities🧡✨

Looking back when I first applied for the FEU IABF Student Council PUBLICITY AND CONTENTS DIVISION, I had no prior background connected to this division. Yet, it did not stop me from applying, learning, and of course loving the work in this division. With PubCon, I have done many things that I never even consider possible to achieve.

Most importantly, the Student Council did not only strengthen my credentials and skills---it also gave me a sense of belonging and purpose. I built connections and lifelong friendships with people who helped me grow both personally and professionally.

With PubCon, I found a passion, I found friends, and I was able to grow. With PubCon, I found a HOME.🫂

IABF SC, you will forever hold a special place in my heart💖

Apply now and be part of FEU IABF SC!
📌IABF SC Application: https://bit.ly/4mQgw3M

Stage of endless possibilities🧡✨

Looking back when I first applied for the FEU IABF Student Council PUBLICITY AND CONTENTS DIVISION, I had no prior background connected to this division. Yet, it did not stop me from applying, learning, and of course loving the work in this division. With PubCon, I have done many things that I never even consider possible to achieve.

Most importantly, the Student Council did not only strengthen my credentials and skills---it also gave me a sense of belonging and purpose. I built connections and lifelong friendships with people who helped me grow both personally and professionally.

message.text:
Stage of endless possibilities🧡✨

Looking back when I first applied for the FEU IABF Student Council PUBLICITY AND CONTENTS DIVISION, I had no prior background connected to this division. Yet, it did not stop me from applying, learning, and of course loving the work in this division. With PubCon, I have done many things that I never even consider possible to achieve.

Most importantly, the Student Council did not only strengthen my credentials and skills---it also gave me a sense of belonging and purpose. I built connections and lifelong friendships with people who helped me grow both personally and professionally.

With PubCon, I found a passion, I found friends, and I was able to grow. With PubCon, I found a HOME.🫂

IABF SC, you will forever hold a special place in my heart💖

Apply now and be part of FEU IABF SC!
📌IABF SC Application: https://bit.ly/4mQgw3M
📌Powerband: https://bit.ly/4gcoxgT
📌PDDC: https://bit.ly/46wHPcL
